text: Desmiphora aegrota is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Bates in 1880. It is known from the United States and Panama.BioLib.cz - Desmiphora aegrota. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Desmiphora Category:Beetles described in 1880
title: Desmiphora aegrota
